BUILD TASKER

You are building Tasker.

Tasker is a cross-platform CLI-first developer productivity tool.

The goal:

Create a universal AI agent workspace protocol where tasks, knowledge, history, and decisions are stored as files so any AI agent or human can continue work without depending on a specific model.

The core principle:

A task is a permanent document.
An agent is a temporary worker.

Agents can be replaced at any time because the task contains all context required.

